      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the helplines. i've talked to them. it doesn't change the fact that my body is basically a prison of nerves. people keep saying \"it gets better\" or \"stay strong\" but they don't get it. they don't understand that sometimes the only thing that would actually help is if everything just... stopped. if there was just peace and no more sensation. it feels like the only way to actually get relief is to stop being here.",
