    "summary": "The user describes experiencing extreme, unmanageable chronic physical pain and expresses suicidal ideation as a desire for relief from suffering. The assistant responds by validating the user's extreme exhaustion and the logic behind their desire to \"give up,\" though it repeatedly includes crisis resource information.",
